<p>
We're also updating Bugzilla to make sorting new bugs into new categories fast
and easy. Soon moving bugs to a new category will be a matter of a few seconds 
and one step. 
</p>
<p>
We can even simplify the triage process with 
<a href="https://github.com/gijsk/triage-helper">the Triage-Helper addon</a>. 
This will let triagers quickly ask contributors for a series of common next 
steps, including reproducing the bug in a clean profile or safe mode, 
narrowing down a test case, and others.
</p>
